37
00:02:17,919 --> 00:02:19,840
of different kinds of insect pests.

38
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:23,759
And here in the United States, it's been estimated that bats

39
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:28,319
provide billions of dollars every year to the US agricultural industry

40
00:02:28,319 --> 00:02:32,159
through their voracious consumption of agricultural pests and sex.

41
00:02:32,159 --> 00:02:36,000
Most bats eat only insects, their insectivores.

42
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:40,239
