59
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:50,960
Of course, you know, the Holy Grail right now for COVID-19 is to discover

60
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:55,920
where is that progenitor virus and also in which kind of animals are human, right?

61
00:03:55,920 --> 00:04:02,800
And usually the progenitor virus has to be 99.9% identical to the outbreak virus.

62
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:07,599
And so our study was set up but to do that, if you can catch that virus,

63
