the Holy Grail. This expression, the Holy Grail, is associated with the cup believed to have been

66
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:33,439
used by Jesus Christ at his last meal. It means something extremely difficult to find or get.

67
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:39,920
If you can discover the progenitor virus, then in the words of Professor Wang, that's brilliant.

68
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:43,439
An exclamation meaning that's very good or amazing.

69
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:49,839
So although bats are sometimes wrongly blamed for causing COVID, they are good friends to farmers,

70
